title: [Market Bend, Black Foot Alley]
description: The alleyway bends from south to east and narrows as an almost triangular wooden building juts into it, ending at a small granite fountain that must have once stood at the center of the road.  A large woman with thick whiskers on her face stands in the doorway of this peculiar building, glaring.
